{"tid":448573,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【短篇童話】【好認真畫】龜兔再賽跑","createTime":"2017-10-26T10:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T10:55:56.000Z","uid":79912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7c918d4491b0ddd8e85e5a4b6ab854ec2328458b","tid":448573,"uid":79912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:34:28.000Z","msg":"Hi! 我是奈樂樂.<br />\n<br />\n我一直都係寫D簡單的短篇故事，<br />\n配上手繪童話式畫風,<br />\n去諷刺(本地)成人世界黑暗醜惡的一面。<br />\n<br />\n第一篇在這裏~<br />\n《恐怖核心與小鳥》<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/OtEG07\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FOtEG07&d=Y7VwzlJytDCaiwRAYbw4abIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=244f5e5a\" target=\"_blank\">goo.gl/OtEG07</a><br />\n<br />\n還有這篇~<br />\n《魔女的謊言》<br />\n<a href=\"http://goo.gl/YJ5mfe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FYJ5mfe&d=Y7VwzlJytDCaiwRAYbw4abIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c3e79bb9\" target=\"_blank\">goo.gl/YJ5mfe</a><br />\n<br />\n因為毎幅也畫很久, 所以出很慢.<br />\n但其實這些畫的質素我還不滿意, <br />\n所以《龜兔再賽跑》之後的故事可能出更慢...<br />\n<br />\n慶幸的是故事都是短篇, 所以大家就可以很快讀完, 又不用等待.<br />\n然我就能慢慢畫另一故事吧~ 我是這樣想的.<br />\n<br />\n各位看完覺得ok就得閒share及like下我的page la~<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nalok.lok/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnalok.lok%2F&d=Y7VwzlJytDCaiwRAYbw4abIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b70aaaf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/nalok.lok/</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nalok.lok/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnalok.lok%2F&d=Y7VwzlJytDCaiwRAYbw4abIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b0b2abad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nalok.lok/</a>"},{"pid":"bca3707c2493deb703b911771cf64fcc31830831","tid":448573,"uid":141495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:37:17.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n好有心，支持樓主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80ed8e2c33179e56220020ace5ef10d8ad2c6e5","tid":